te fire ukene, s\u00e5 det sp\u00f8rs hvor lenge det varer n\u00e5. Forh\u00e5pentligvis er alt i orden, sier Kolstad.", "Otis AS har ikke lyst til \u00e5 kommentere saken ytterligere."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "0a174ba8f25d4d2a17fc929ec15d0a2dc0d1338929976225c31d167b9e37466c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-28T22:10:26.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Men n\u00e5 ser det ut til at det endelig ordner seg for beboerne i h\u00f8yblokka p\u00e5 Valentinlyst i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1343874.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/valentinlyst"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/3875729752c00f2f687dbdf59aaf52d5d4565e94.jpg?594fdd7d"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Heistr\u00f8bbel har isolert beboere i fire uker -adressa.no", "Isolert i blokka", "B\u00e5reheis ute av drift", "Fikset i kveld"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "3875729752c00f2f687dbdf59aaf52d5d4565e94"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "sports"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "otis as"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["heisen", "beboerne", "blokka", "beboer", "isolert beboere", "uker"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["valentinlystsenteret", "valentinlyst"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["stig tore johansen", "otis midt-norge", "bj\u00f8rn kolstad"]}, {"field":